            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For, while we are feasting here,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Starving millions, far and near,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Call us with the bitter cry:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come and help us, or we die."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In this day of full increase,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Shall we, can we, hold our peace?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Staying here we do not well;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now then, let us go and tell:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Tell how He hath set us free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How He leads triumphantly;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How He satisfies our need;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How His rest is rest indeed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Speak, for we, Thy servants, hear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou hast taught us not to fear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And whate’er Thy word shall be,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
